Research Council.  Annual subscriptions are available for $15.
Contact:  Family Research Council, 700 Thirteenth St., N.W.,
Suite 500, Washington, D.C. 20005.  Phone:  202-393-2100.  President:
Gary L. Bauer; Editor:  William R. Mattox, Jr.; Editorial and
Production Support:  Anne Redd, Rosanne Dupras, Deanna Carlson,
Charles A. Donovan, Valerie Stambaugh; Distribution:  Kevin Gilliam,
