<DOCNO>WT16-B21-38</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA024-000258-B012-14</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/pff/mip/3a.html 204.71.237.86 19970108153837 text/html 10355
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 15:38:55 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:10 GMT
