<DOCOLDNO>IA024-000258-B015-246</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/pff/tr-1b.html 204.71.237.86 19970108155205 text/html 10993
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
